data.description: This home is immaculate! Located in a gated 55+ plus community, this nearly 1200 square foot home shows true pride of ownership. Flooring in most of the home is newer, as are most faucets. Home has a full home water softener, and a reverse osmosis for drinking water. Another unique aspect of this home is the shed is wired for electricity and is finished inside. Granite countertops, window tint and coverings throughout home. This primary bedroom boasts a HUGE walk in closet. Call today to see this beauty!
